Name: Synth Swinger
About the game: Are you Ready to Swing? This upcoming first-person platformer very much has the visual appeal and sheer electricity of gameplay. As for its mechanics, it will feature swinging via grapple, jumping, and wall-running, all of which are set in an amazing neo-lit world. Early Access Includes Full playable game and training area for you to further explore your skills.
